<div class="customer-reviews-section section section--{{ section.settings.section_width }}" style="--customer-reviews-bg-image: url('{{ "review_bg.png" | asset_url }}');">
  <div class="customer-reviews__inner">
    <div class="customer-reviews__header">
      <p class="customer-reviews__eyebrow">CUSTOMER LOVE</p>
      <h2 class="customer-reviews__heading">Customers Are Saying</h2>
      <p class="customer-reviews__rating" aria-label="4.8 out of 5 from 500 plus happy customers">
        <span class="customer-reviews__stars" aria-hidden="true">★★★★★</span>
        <span class="customer-reviews__rating-text">4.8/5 from 500+ happy customers</span>
      </p>
      <p class="customer-reviews__subheading">
        Real reviews from real customers who love our personalized bedding.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="customer-reviews__grid">
      <article class="customer-reviews__card">
        <div class="customer-reviews__person">
          <div class="customer-reviews__avatar customer-reviews__avatar--jessica" aria-hidden="true">JM</div>
          <div class="customer-reviews__meta">
            <h3 class="customer-reviews__name">Jessica M.</h3>
            <p class="customer-reviews__verified">Verified Buyer</p>
            <p class="customer-reviews__card-stars" aria-hidden="true">★★★★★</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="customer-reviews__body">
          The custom quilt I ordered for my son turned out even better than I expected. The colors are 
          vibrant, the stitching is perfect, and it’s so soft and cozy. He loves seeing his name on it
          every night.
        </p>
        <div class="customer-reviews__product">
          <div class="customer-reviews__product-thumb customer-reviews__product-thumb--patchwork"></div>
          <div class="customer-reviews__product-copy">
            <p class="customer-reviews__product-title">Personalized Patchwork Quilt</p>
            <p class="customer-reviews__product-meta">Twin • Michael</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="customer-reviews__card">
        <div class="customer-reviews__person">
          <div class="customer-reviews__avatar customer-reviews__avatar--amanda" aria-hidden="true">AR</div>
          <div class="customer-reviews__meta">
            <h3 class="customer-reviews__name">Amanda R.</h3>
            <p class="customer-reviews__verified">Verified Buyer</p>
            <p class="customer-reviews__card-stars" aria-hidden="true">★★★★★</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="customer-reviews__body">
          Absolutely love our new duvet set! The fabric feels luxurious and the personalized embroidery 
          makes it so special. Shipping was fast and the packaging was beautiful. Will definitely order
          again!
        </p>
        <div class="customer-reviews__product">
          <div class="customer-reviews__product-thumb customer-reviews__product-thumb--duvet"></div>
          <div class="customer-reviews__product-copy">
            <p class="customer-reviews__product-title">Embroidered Duvet Set</p>
            <p class="customer-reviews__product-meta">Queen • Our Initials</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="customer-reviews__card">
        <div class="customer-reviews__person">
          <div class="customer-reviews__avatar customer-reviews__avatar--rachel" aria-hidden="true">RT</div>
          <div class="customer-reviews__meta">
            <h3 class="customer-reviews__name">Rachel T.</h3>
            <p class="customer-reviews__verified">Verified Buyer</p>
            <p class="customer-reviews__card-stars" aria-hidden="true">★★★★★</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="customer-reviews__body">
          This blanket is the perfect gift! The quality is amazing and the personalization makes it so 
          meaningful. My sister cried when she saw it. Highly recommend for any special occasion.
        </p>
        <div class="customer-reviews__product">
          <div class="customer-reviews__product-thumb customer-reviews__product-thumb--blanket"></div>
          <div class="customer-reviews__product-copy">
            <p class="customer-reviews__product-title">Personalized Sherpa Blanket</p>
            <p class="customer-reviews__product-meta">60&quot; × 80&quot; • Sophia</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="customer-reviews__card">
        <div class="customer-reviews__person">
          <div class="customer-reviews__avatar customer-reviews__avatar--sarah" aria-hidden="true">SL</div>
          <div class="customer-reviews__meta">
            <h3 class="customer-reviews__name">Sarah L.</h3>
            <p class="customer-reviews__verified">Verified Buyer</p>
            <p class="customer-reviews__card-stars" aria-hidden="true">★★★★★</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="customer-reviews__body">
          We ordered a personalized comforter for our guest room and it instantly made the space feel 
          warmer and more special. The finish is beautiful, the fabric feels cozy, and the custom touch
          looks so elegant.
        </p>
        <div class="customer-reviews__product">
          <div class="customer-reviews__product-thumb customer-reviews__product-thumb--comforter"></div>
          <div class="customer-reviews__product-copy">
            <p class="customer-reviews__product-title">Custom Comforter Set</p>
            <p class="customer-reviews__product-meta">King • Guest Room</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% stylesheet %}
  .customer-reviews-section {
    position: relative;
    isolation: isolate;
    padding-block: clamp(2.4rem, 4.8vw, 3.5rem);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .customer-reviews-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: -2;
    pointer-events: none;
    background-color: #f6efe8;
    background-image: var(--customer-reviews-bg-image, none);
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
  }

  .customer-reviews-section::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: -1;
    pointer-events: none;
    background: rgb(255 248 239 / 0.12);
  }

  .customer-reviews__inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    width: min(100%, 1200px);
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding-inline: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
  }

  .customer-reviews__header {
    max-width: 40rem;
    margin: 0 auto clamp(1.35rem, 2.8vw, 2rem);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .customer-reviews__eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 0.55rem;
    color: #9d6c4f;
    font-size: clamp(0.74rem, 0.92vw, 0.86rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  }

  .customer-reviews__heading {
    margin: 0;
    color: #3f2e24;
    font-family: var(--font-heading--family);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.1vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .customer-reviews__rating {
    display: inline-flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    margin: 0.7rem 0 0;
    color: #5a4030;
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.15vw, 1rem);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .customer-reviews__stars,
  .customer-reviews__card-stars {
    color: #b87345;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  }

  .customer-reviews__subheading {
    margin: 0.65rem auto 0;
    max-width: 31rem;
    color: #6f594a;
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1vw, 0.98rem);
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .customer-reviews__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: clamp(0.7rem, 1.1vw, 0.9rem);
  }

  .customer-reviews__card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: clamp(0.8rem, 1.1vw, 0.95rem);
    border: 1px solid rgb(214 187 163 / 0.7);
    border-radius: 1.6rem;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgb(255 250 245 / 0.8) 0%, rgb(249 240 231 / 0.9) 100%);
    box-shadow:
      0 1px 0 rgb(255 255 255 / 0.65) inset,
      0 14px 28px rgb(110 80 61 / 0.08);
    backdrop-filter: blur(3px);
  }

  .customer-reviews__person {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.65rem;
  }

  .customer-reviews__avatar {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    width: 3.3rem;
    height: 3.3rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    color: #fff9f4;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%, rgb(255 255 255 / 0.55), transparent 30%), linear-gradient(135deg, #d4ae95, #8a6248);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgb(95 70 53 / 0.14);
  }

  .customer-reviews__avatar--amanda {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%, rgb(255 255 255 / 0.55), transparent 30%), linear-gradient(135deg, #c9967b, #6c4a36);
  }

  .customer-reviews__avatar--rachel {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%, rgb(255 255 255 / 0.55), transparent 30%), linear-gradient(135deg, #d2a48c, #7f5841);
  }

  .customer-reviews__avatar--sarah {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 30%, rgb(255 255 255 / 0.55), transparent 30%), linear-gradient(135deg, #d8b395, #8e6448);
  }

  .customer-reviews__name {
    margin: 0;
    color: #4d382a;
    font-family: var(--font-heading--family);
    font-size: clamp(1.12rem, 1.3vw, 1.35rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .customer-reviews__verified {
    margin: 0.15rem 0 0;
    color: #7d6657;
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .customer-reviews__card-stars {
    margin: 0.28rem 0 0;
    font-size: 0.76rem;
  }

  .customer-reviews__body {
    margin: 0;
    color: #5f493a;
    font-size: clamp(0.78rem, 0.82vw, 0.84rem);
    line-height: 1.38;
  }

  .customer-reviews__product {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-top: auto;
    padding: 0.45rem;
    border: 1px solid rgb(220 199 180 / 0.72);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: rgb(255 247 239 / 0.58);
    box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgb(255 255 255 / 0.55) inset;
  }

  .customer-reviews__product-thumb {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    width: 2.85rem;
    height: 2.85rem;
    border-radius: 0.85rem;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgb(82 58 44 / 0.08);
  }

  .customer-reviews__product-thumb--patchwork {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d9b38e, #8c5e41 60%, #4d3326);
  }

  .customer-reviews__product-thumb--duvet {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f1e3d5, #d7c0ab 55%, #b79273);
  }

  .customer-reviews__product-thumb--blanket {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4a3a7, #bb8a90 52%, #8f6167);
  }

  .customer-reviews__product-thumb--comforter {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dfc4af, #bf9b80 52%, #8c6349);
  }

  .customer-reviews__product-title,
  .customer-reviews__product-meta {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .customer-reviews__product-title {
    color: #584233;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.22;
  }

  .customer-reviews__product-meta {
    margin-top: 0.12rem;
    color: #8d7768;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    line-height: 1.22;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 1199px) {
    .customer-reviews__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .customer-reviews__card {
      gap: 0.8rem;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .customer-reviews-section {
      padding-block: 2.1rem;
    }

    .customer-reviews__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .customer-reviews__person {
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .customer-reviews__avatar {
      width: 3.75rem;
      height: 3.75rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .customer-reviews__name {
      font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 6vw, 1.55rem);
    }
  }
{% endstylesheet %}

{% schema %}
  {
    "name": "Customer reviews",
    "settings": [
      {
        "type": "select",
        "id": "section_width",
        "label": "Section width",
        "default": "page-width",
        "options": [
          {
            "value": "page-width",
            "label": "Page width"
          }, {
            "value": "full-width",
            "label": "Full width"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "presets": [
      {
        "name": "Customer reviews"
      }
    ]
  }
{% endschema %}
